<problem id="fs-id1167133457029">
<para id="fs-id1167133457032">A concave mirror of radius of curvature 10 cm is placed 30 cm from a thin convex lens of focal length 15 cm. Find the location and magnification of a small bulb sitting 50 cm from the lens by using the algebraic method.</para>
