<solution id="fs-id1167133339351">
<para id="fs-id1167132317526">12 cm to the left of the mirror, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>m</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mtext>/</m:mtext><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></para>
