<para id="fs-id1167133859129">Copy and trace how a horizontal ray from <emphasis effect="italics">S</emphasis> comes out after the lens. Use <m:math><m:mrow><m:mi>n</m:mi><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>1.55</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> for the glass.</para>
