<exercise id="fs-id1167132247395">
<problem id="fs-id1167132247397">
<para id="fs-id1167132354381">A 3 cm tall object is placed 5 cm in front of a convex mirror of radius of curvature 20 cm. Where is the image formed? How tall is the image? What is the orientation of the image?</para>
